---
---
  <section
    id="page-hero"
    class="relative grid min-h-[70vh] grid-cols-1 overflow-hidden bg-dark-red pt-[var(--nav-h)] lg:grid-cols-2"
  >
    <div class="relative z-[2] flex flex-col justify-end px-5 pb-20 pt-12 md:px-10 md:pb-20 md:pl-20 lg:py-20 lg:pl-20 lg:pr-[60px]">
      <div class="mb-7 flex items-center gap-2.5 font-body text-[10px] tracking-[0.3em] text-blush uppercase">
        <a class="text-gray-orange transition-colors hover:text-cream" href="/">Home</a>
        <span class="opacity-40">/</span>
        <span class="text-cream">About</span>
      </div>
      <h1 class="mb-4 font-display text-[clamp(36px,5vw,68px)] leading-[1.05] tracking-[0.35em] text-cream uppercase">
        ABOUT<br />ELAMRIT
      </h1>
      <p class="max-w-[400px] font-serif text-xl italic leading-relaxed text-cream/70">
        The story behind the feast — our origins, our craft, and the people who bring it all to life.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="relative hidden overflow-hidden lg:block">
      <div class="ph-image absolute inset-0 min-h-[50vh] lg:min-h-full"></div>
      <div
        class="absolute right-[60px] bottom-[60px] z-[3] max-w-[280px] border-l-[3px] border-green bg-[color-mix(in_srgb,var(--dark-red)_92%,black)] px-8 py-7 backdrop-blur-md"
      >
        <p class="mb-3 font-serif text-[17px] italic leading-relaxed text-cream">
          "We don't just cater events. We compose experiences that become memories."
        </p>
        <div class="font-body text-[10px] tracking-[0.2em] text-gray-orange uppercase">— Elamrit Philosophy</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
